---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="pt-36 pb-20 bg-carbon-canvas">
    <div class="page-container text-center">
      <div class="section-title-block">
        <p class="section-title-label">Company</p>
        <h1 class="section-title-main section-title-main-lg">About Uroo.dev</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="font-circularxx font-regular text-body-sm tracking-body-sm text-smoke max-w-xl mx-auto">A modern software house built for the digital age.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap bg-carbon-canvas">
    <div class="page-container max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading tracking-heading text-bone-white mb-6">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 font-circularxx font-regular text-body-sm tracking-body-sm text-smoke leading-body-sm">
        <p>Uroo.dev was founded with a simple mission: help businesses and startups solve their operational and digital challenges through custom software solutions that actually work.</p>
        <p>We believe that great software comes from understanding the problem first, then applying the right technology to solve it. Not the other way around.</p>
        <p>Every project starts with a question: "What problem are we solving?" The answer to that question guides everything we do.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap bg-ash-veil">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="showcase-card text-center">
          <h3 class="font-circularxx font-medium text-caption tracking-caption text-iron-gray mb-4 uppercase">Mission</h3>
          <p class="font-circularxx font-regular text-caption tracking-caption text-carbon-canvas leading-caption">Deliver high-quality, scalable software that solves real business problems and drives measurable growth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-card text-center">
          <h3 class="font-circularxx font-medium text-caption tracking-caption text-iron-gray mb-4 uppercase">Vision</h3>
          <p class="font-circularxx font-regular text-caption tracking-caption text-carbon-canvas leading-caption">Be the most trusted software partner for businesses across Southeast Asia.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-card text-center">
          <h3 class="font-circularxx font-medium text-caption tracking-caption text-iron-gray mb-4 uppercase">Values</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 font-circularxx font-regular text-caption tracking-caption text-carbon-canvas text-left max-w-fit mx-auto">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-carbon-canvas rounded-full"></span>Transparency in every interaction</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-carbon-canvas rounded-full"></span>Quality over quantity</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-carbon-canvas rounded-full"></span>Client success is our success</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap bg-carbon-canvas">
    <div class="page-container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading tracking-heading text-bone-white text-center mb-10">The Founder</h2>
      <div class="review-card text-center max-w-lg mx-auto">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-bone-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5" style="border-radius: 9999px;">
          <span class="font-circularxx font-medium text-lg text-carbon-canvas">DI</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-circularxx font-medium text-body-sm tracking-body-sm text-bone-white mb-1">Dimas Irawan</h3>
        <p class="review-card-attribution mb-4">Founder & Lead Developer</p>
        <p class="review-card-quote text-sm">With years of experience building digital products, Dimas founded Uroo.dev to help businesses leverage technology for growth. His approach combines technical excellence with a deep understanding of business needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
